---

# Recommendations

### Recommendation 1

Store credentials securely outside the source code using environment variables or a secure secrets management solution.

---

### Recommendation 2

Never store passwords in plain text. Store password hashes generated using a modern password hashing algorithm.

---

### Recommendation 3

Implement rate limiting or temporary account lockout after repeated failed login attempts.

---

### Recommendation 4

Use an established authentication framework or identity provider rather than implementing authentication logic manually.

---

### Recommendation 5

Log authentication events securely while avoiding the logging of sensitive information such as passwords.

